(low prio) Because the parameters are same for these two, you can use ensure_resources + hash of parameters to make this more simple.


$listen_opts = {
  'listen_tls' => { 'value' => $listen_tls },
  ...
}

if ! modular_libvirt_real {
  create_resources('libvirtd_config', $listen_opts)
} else {
  create_resources('virtproxyd_config', $listen_opts)
}
